works.description: If you are looking for a unique and beautiful way to store and showcase your wine, you would love to take a look at the innovative wine racks from The Barrel Rack. Chet Bassetti, co-owner of the firm, has been now awarded a U.S. patent for the new wine racks that he makes from old wine barrels. Chet Bassetti, who is a wine-loving inventor and retired engineer, runs The Barrel Rack along with his wife Diane Bassetti. His new design raises the bar for wine enthusiasts and connoisseurs. The man has waited four years for this patent
